data.title: Railway Stations of Kalka Shimla Section & Its Attractions
data.meta_description: 6.pdf - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document describes various stations along the Kalka Shimla railway section of India, providing details about each station such as distance from Kalka, elevation, nearby attractions, and historical information. It discusses 26 stations from Kalka to Shimla, describing the landscape, landmarks, and interesting facts about each location along the 95.57km rail route.
